result.notes: This map identifies areas that offer potential development opportunities for future offshore wind farms. For further information about how this map was derived please refer to the Round 3 map guide. Notes: 1. This layer represents The Crown Estate's present view of locations for potential zones for the development of offshore wind farms. 2. It will be subject to revision. 3. The zones do not in any way reflect the output of BERR's SEA.
